& [SLMFacultyValidationStabilizationContract] is the glyph stabilization authority contract
  + [contract_uuid] is 6c41a783-8ff0-444c-a337-385b05628198
  + [slice_id] is SLM-08
  + [depends_on] is SLM_Provider_Deliberation_Contract, SLM_Wobble_Contradiction_Contract, SLM_Semantic_Diffusion_Pass_Contract
  + [status] is accepted_for_graph_contracts

  & [StabilizationProposal] is a candidate semantic identity submitted for faculty review
    + [proposal_id] is unique in EvidenceWorkspace
    + [candidate_ref] is CandidateMeaning or CandidateRelation
    + [support_sources] is required and must be at least one
    + [wobble_vector] is required
    + [contradiction_set] is required
    + [lineage] is required
    + [provider_deliberation_ref] is optional
    + [provider_faculty_report_refs] are optional lower-provider internal faculty traces

  & [FacultyRun] is the seven-faculty validation record
    + [faculty_run_id] is unique per StabilizationProposal
    + [ObserverVote] is presence validation
    + [HonestyVote] is support sufficiency validation
    + [SecurityVote] is invalid or unsafe consequence validation
    + [PlannerVote] is sequence or task fit validation
    + [WeaverVote] is relational coherence validation
    + [ScribeVote] is lineage preservation validation
    + [RefinerVote] is compression without distortion validation
    + [observer_coordination] is Observer manages Planner, Weaver, Scribe, and Refiner unless vetoed
    + [honesty_veto] is optional blocking veto
    + [security_veto] is optional blocking veto
    = must: record each faculty result as approve, reject, abstain, or needs_more_evidence
    = must: preserve rationale for reject, abstain, needs_more_evidence, and veto

  & [StabilizationDecision] is the promotion gate result
    + [decision] is promote_glyph, create_uncertainty_glyph, preserve_in_evidence_workspace, or reject_candidate
    + [faculty_vote_count] is required
    + [faculty_threshold] is required
    + [contradiction_score] is required
    + [contradiction_threshold] is required
    + [wobble_score] is required
    + [wobble_threshold] is required
    + [lineage_present] is required
    = must: promote_glyph only when support, faculty threshold, contradiction, wobble, and lineage gates pass
    = must: create_uncertainty_glyph only when partial convergence has stable uncertainty boundaries
    = must: preserve_in_evidence_workspace when contradiction remains or uncertainty is unbounded
    - never: promote because support_weight is high by itself

  ! [Slice08Complete] is accepted
    @ [support] stabilization contract defines faculty votes, vetoes, thresholds, and outcomes
    @ [support_delta] SLM-27 separates provider-internal faculty evidence from SLM stabilization authority
